.TH START_PQR 1 "2026-05-15" "v1.02" "PQR Mesh Boot"
.SH NAME
start_pqr \- Automated boot sequence for the PQR Sovereign Mesh
.SH SYNOPSIS
.\start_pqr.ps1
.SH DESCRIPTION
start_pqr is the primary PowerShell bootstrapper. It verifies Docker connectivity, cleans orphan containers, and lifts the entire stack (DB, Vault, Tunnel, Server).
